{
  "texts": [
    "Benchmarks which require training on multiple, independent subsamples would expose training variance.",
    "This paper does not study semi-supervised methods like Pattern-Exploiting Training, or handinspecting the test set text and targeting interventions accordingly.",
    "We also do not study the effect of including unlabeled test set texts in the initial pretraining stage of an LLM.",
    "The results are empirical.",
    "There may be tasks where an evaluation bias exists, and these were not part of the 25 classification tasks we collected."
  ]
}